### Source resolution ‚ÄĒ Agent OS (thin-client)

AGENT_OS_SOURCE=/mnt/work/Projects/.ai

**Rule (before reading any `.ai/...` path):**
1. `.cursorrules` + `.work/**` ‚ÄĒ always local.
2. **Thin-client** (`AGENT_OS_SOURCE` set + readable): read every other `.ai/<path>` from `$AGENT_OS_SOURCE/<path>`.
3. **Fat-client** (unset): read `.ai/<path>` locally.
4. App code resolves locally.
5. **Unreachable source:** stop ‚ÄĒ `agent-os source unreachable: $AGENT_OS_SOURCE` (do not fall back to local leftovers).

