- **`.ai/`:** framework-only (via `$AGENT_OS_SOURCE` in thin-client).
- **`.work/`:** all project memory ‚ÄĒ plans, SPECs, ADRs, `HANDOFF.md`, `PROTECTED_SURFACES.json`, `.work/standards/`, `.work/docs/` (+ `integration/`).

